The kusudama isn't here!

310
00:15:36,694 --> 00:15:37,634
The kusudama?

311
00:15:37,634 --> 00:15:38,534
Huh?

312
00:15:38,534 --> 00:15:39,364
Oh no!

313
00:15:39,364 --> 00:15:40,194
What?!

314
00:15:41,634 --> 00:15:44,374
I'm sorry! I forgot the all-important kusudama!

315
00:15:44,374 --> 00:15:45,744
Save the regrets for later.

316
00:15:45,744 --> 00:15:47,574
We have less than an hour
before the festivities start.

317
00:15:47,574 --> 00:15:48,544
Right!

318
00:15:51,314 --> 00:15:52,614
Tokuno?!

319
00:15:52,614 --> 00:15:56,654
The Traffic Section's gone,
so I'm watching the office.

320
00:15:56,654 --> 00:16:00,314
Thank you for your help.
We came back for something we forgot.

321
00:16:00,724 --> 00:16:02,754
Here it is! Thank goodness!

322
00:16:02,754 --> 00:16:04,324
Saori, hurry!

323
00:16:04,324 --> 00:16:05,294
Right!

324
00:16:05,294 --> 00:16:08,094
Good grief. Never a dull moment
at the Traffic Section.

325
00:16:09,934 --> 00:16:11,564
Do you think we'll make it in time?

326
00:16:11,564 --> 00:16:13,194
By the skin of our teeth.

327
00:16:14,004 --> 00:16:16,074
A traffic jam? All the way here?

328
00:16:16,074 --> 00:16:17,094
Oh no!

329
00:16:24,614 --> 00:16:25,814
Traffic Section.

330
00:16:25,814 --> 00:16:28,954
Tokuno? Did Miyuki get there yet?

331
00:16:28,954 --> 00:16:30,284
A few minutes ago.

332
00:16:30,284 --> 00:16:33,384
The streets headed in this direction
are backed up solid!

333
00:16:33,384 --> 00:16:34,654
That's not good.

334
00:16:34,654 --> 00:16:37,424
They might not make it back in time.

335
00:16:37,424 --> 00:16:38,764
Don't worry.

336
00:16:38,764 --> 00:16:43,264
You've always found some way to
come through no matter what.

337
00:16:43,264 --> 00:16:44,964
Huh? Tokuno?

338
00:16:45,164 --> 00:16:47,864
That's how it is here at Traffic Section, right?

339
00:16:51,344 --> 00:16:55,144
We're not going to make it!
I'll carry it there myself!

340
00:16:55,144 --> 00:16:57,274
Wait! There has to be a way.

341
00:16:57,274 --> 00:16:58,184
But...

342
00:16:58,184 --> 00:16:59,974
Don't give up until the very end!

343
00:17:01,214 --> 00:17:02,314
If we detour around this street...

344
00:17:02,314 --> 00:17:03,484
I might be able to...

345
00:17:03,484 --> 00:17:05,884
But there are more cars than normal.

346
00:17:07,084 --> 00:17:09,454
A motorcycle! That's it... I'll call Nakajima.

347
00:17:11,564 --> 00:17:13,964
Working hard, Traffic Section?

348
00:17:15,234 --> 00:17:16,464
Need help?

349
00:17:16,464 --> 00:17:17,434
Natsumi?!

350
00:17:17,434 --> 00:17:18,764
Natsumi Senpai?!

351
00:17:18,764 --> 00:17:22,304
They said the bridge was completed,
so I wanted to cross it.

352
00:17:22,304 --> 00:17:24,404
I insisted on a day off and
went to the Traffic Section.

353
00:17:24,404 --> 00:17:26,704
Then Detective Tokuno said you had
some sort of emergency,

354
00:17:26,704 --> 00:17:28,744
so I grabbed this and came after you.

355
00:17:28,744 --> 00:17:30,514
You should've called!

356
00:17:30,514 --> 00:17:33,344
That's right! We were all worried about you!

357
00:17:33,344 --> 00:17:37,054
Sorry, sorry. I didn't mean to keep it
a secret or anything.

358
00:17:37,054 --> 00:17:39,254
Natsumi, are you wearing your uniform?

359
00:17:39,254 --> 00:17:42,794
Yeah, don't know why, but there was
a clean one in my locker.

360
00:17:42,794 --> 00:17:45,454
Thought I'd wear it for old times' sake.
Was that wrong of me?

361
00:17:46,864 --> 00:17:49,564
That's the one we washed
because it was growing mold...

362
00:17:49,564 --> 00:17:50,794
What?

363
00:17:52,034 --> 00:17:53,834
What's so funny?!

364
00:17:53,834 --> 00:17:57,004
It's nothing! We don't have much time.

365
00:17:57,004 --> 00:17:57,974
Natsumi!

366
00:18:01,044 --> 00:18:02,034
Did I make it in time?

367
00:18:02,614 --> 00:18:03,444
This street.

368
00:18:03,444 --> 00:18:05,884
I know. The one we always covered.

369
00:18:05,884 --> 00:18:08,784
Traffic is heavy today, so be careful.

370
00:18:08,784 --> 00:18:09,814
Okay!

371
00:18:09,814 --> 00:18:10,844
